Subject: [PATCH 1/2] fix(rfork): support quantized model transfer

Align receiver tensors with Ascend post-load quantized layouts before RFork transfer.

- vLLM version: v0.20.2
- vLLM main:
https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/commit/9090368b650896bf5fc990c921df7eb4c20355a5

